<hr>
<h2 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-3.SolutionArchitecture">3. =
Solution Architecture</h2>
<h3 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-3.1ArchitectureConstraintsa=
ndAssumptions">3.1 Architecture Constraints and Assumptions</h3>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-3.1.1Constraints">3.1.1 Con=
straints</h4>
<ul>
 <li><strong>Version check</strong>: <code>omnia.sh --upgrade</code> only p=
roceeds when the detected core container is 1.0 (Omnia 2.0 code) and the ta=
rget manifest advertises 1.1 (Omnia 2.1 code).</li>
 <li><strong>Backups</strong>: Timestamped directories (default <code>/opt/=
omnia/backups/upgrade_&lt;timestamp&gt;</code>) must reside on a writable f=
ilesystem with =E2=89=A52 GB free space.</li>
 <li><strong>Note</strong>: <code>/opt/omnia</code> is a directory inside t=
he Omnia core container, mounted as a persistent volume from the OIM host.<=
/li>
 <li><strong>User approval gate</strong>: The script prompts operators with=
 the list of new features and requires confirmation before stopping service=
s and swapping containers.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-3.1.2Assumptions">3.1.2 Ass=
umptions</h4>
<ul>
 <li>Administrator has sudo/root access on the OIM node and can run <code>o=
mnia.sh</code>.</li>
 <li>Network connectivity to Docker Hub is available for pulling the 1.1 im=
age.</li>
 <li>Existing SSH keys, inputs, and provisioning data remain mounted under =
<code>/opt/omnia</code>.</li>
 <li>Downtime window of 5=E2=80=9310 minutes is acceptable for the apply st=
age.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-3.2ArchitectureControlFlow"=
>3.2 Architecture Control Flow</h3>
<p><code>omnia.sh --upgrade</code> orchestrates the upgrade through a compr=
ehensive six-phase workflow. The script pulls the tagged Omnia core 1.1 con=
tainer (Omnia 2.1 code) from Docker Hub unless that image already exists lo=
cally.</p>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-3.2.1UpgradeWorkflowPhases"=
>3.2.1 Upgrade Workflow Phases</h4>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">+-------------------------------------------------=
----------------------------+
|                        OMNIA UPGRADE WORKFLOW                            =
   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------=
---+
|                                                                          =
   |
|  +--------------+    +--------------+    +--------------+                =
   |
|  |   PHASE 1    |---&gt;|   PHASE 2    |---&gt;|   PHASE 3    |          =
         |
|  | Pre-Upgrade  |    |   Approval   |    |    Backup    |                =
   |
|  |  Validation  |    |     Gate     |    |   Creation   |                =
   |
|  +--------------+    +--------------+    +--------------+                =
   |
|         |                   |                   |                        =
   |
|         v                   v                   v                        =
   |
|    [Fail: Exit]       [Reject: Exit]     [Fail: Exit]                    =
   |
|                                                 |                        =
   |
|                                                 v                        =
   |
|  +--------------+    +--------------+    +--------------+                =
   |
|  |   PHASE 6    |&lt;---|   PHASE 5    |&lt;---|   PHASE 4    |          =
         |
|  | Post-Upgrade |    |  Migration   |    |  Container   |                =
   |
|  |  Validation  |    |   &amp; Apply    |    |    Swap      |            =
       |
|  +--------------+    +--------------+    +--------------+                =
   |
|         |                   |                   |                        =
   |
|         v                   v                   v                        =
   |
|    [Success]          [Fail: Rollback]   [Fail: Rollback]                =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------=
---+
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-3.2.2PhaseDetails">3.2.2 Ph=
ase Details</h4>
<p><strong>Phase 1: Pre-Upgrade Validation</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Step</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Action</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Failure Handling</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">1.1</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Detect running container version (must be 1.=
0)</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Exit with error if version mismatch</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">1.4</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Validate existing /opt/omnia mount and permi=
ssions</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Exit with mount/permission fix instructions<=
/td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">1.5</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Pull 1.1 image if not present locally</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Exit with manual pull instructions on failur=
e</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<p><strong>Phase 2: Approval Gate</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Step</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Action</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Failure Handling</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">2.1</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Display current Omnia version (2.0) and targ=
et version (2.1)</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">N/A</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">2.2</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">List new features in Omnia 2.1</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">N/A</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">2.3</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Display breaking changes and migration impac=
ts</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">N/A</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">2.4</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Prompt for backup destination (default: /opt=
/omnia/backups/upgrade_timestamp)</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Use default if empty</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">2.5</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Update upgrade directory in metadata file</t=
d>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><br></td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">2.6</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Require explicit user confirmation (y/N)</td=
>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Exit gracefully on rejection</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<p><strong>Phase 3: Backup Creation</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Step</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Action</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Failure Handling</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">3.1</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Create timestamped backup directory</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Exit if directory creation fails</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">3.2</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Backup input files from /opt/omnia/input/</t=
d>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Rollback: remove partial backup</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">3.3</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Backup container configuration files</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Rollback: remove partial backup</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">3.4</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Backup oim_metadata.yml</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Rollback: remove partial backup</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">3.5</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Generate backup manifest</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Rollback: remove partial backup</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">3.6</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Verify backup integrity</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Exit if verification fails</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<p><strong>Phase 4: Container Swap</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Step</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Action</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Failure Handling</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">4.1</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Stop Omnia core 1.0 container gracefully</td=
>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">4.2</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Verify 1.0 container stopped</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback (force stop)</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">4.3</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Start Omnia core 1.1 Quadlet unit</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">4.4</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Wait for 1.1 container health check (timeout=
: 60s)</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">4.5</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Update /opt/omnia/.data/oim_metadata.yml wit=
h omnia_version: 2.1.0.0</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<p><strong>Phase 5: Migration and Apply (Inside Core 1.1 Container)</strong=
></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Step</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Action</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Failure Handling</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">5.1</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Execute upgrade_omnia.yml playbook inside Co=
re 1.1 container</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">5.2</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Call upgrade_oim.yml to transform inputs 2.0=
 to 2.1</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">5.3</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Read existing 2.0 input files from /opt/omni=
a/input/</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">5.4</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Transform and write 2.1 compatible input fil=
es</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">5.5</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Call upgrade_cluster.yml to generate reprovi=
sion guidance</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">5.6</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Validate migrated input file syntax</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
