<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-3.2.3RollbackWorkflow">3.2.=
3 Rollback Workflow</h4>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">+-------------------------------------------------=
----------------------------+
|                        OMNIA ROLLBACK WORKFLOW                           =
   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------=
---+
|                                                                          =
   |
|  Trigger: omnia.sh --rollback OR Automatic on upgrade failure            =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
|  +--------------+    +--------------+    +--------------+                =
   |
|  |   STEP 1     |---&gt;|   STEP 2     |---&gt;|   STEP 3     |          =
         |
|  |   Validate   |    |   Stop 1.1   |    |  Restore     |                =
   |
|  |   Backup     |    |  Container   |    |   Inputs     |                =
   |
|  +--------------+    +--------------+    +--------------+                =
   |
|                                                 |                        =
   |
|                                                 v                        =
   |
|  +--------------+    +--------------+    +--------------+                =
   |
|  |   STEP 6     |&lt;---|   STEP 5     |&lt;---|   STEP 4     |          =
         |
|  |   Validate   |    |   Update     |    |  Start 1.0   |                =
   |
|  |   Rollback   |    |  Metadata    |    |  Container   |                =
   |
|  +--------------+    +--------------+    +--------------+                =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------=
---+
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Rollback Steps:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Step</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Action</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">1</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Validate backup exists</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Locate latest backup in <code>/opt/omnia/bac=
kups/</code> or user-specified path</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">2</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Stop 1.1 container</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Gracefully stop the upgraded container (forc=
e if needed)</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">3</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Execute <code>rollback_omnia.yml</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Restore input files from backup</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">4</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Start 1.0 container</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Restart the original Quadlet unit</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">5</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Update metadata</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Revert <code>oim_metadata.yml</code> to <cod=
e>omnia_version: 2.0.0.0</code></td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">6</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Validate rollback</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Verify 1.0 container health and input access=
ibility</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-3.2.4InstallConflictHandlin=
g">3.2.4 Install Conflict Handling</h4>
<p>If <code>omnia.sh --install</code> is run while a 1.0 core container is =
detected:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">+-------------------------------------------------=
----------------------------+
|  ERROR: Existing Omnia 2.0 installation detected.                        =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
|  Cannot proceed with fresh install while existing installation is present=
.  |
|                                                                          =
   |
|  To upgrade:  Run 'omnia.sh --upgrade' to upgrade to Omnia 2.1           =
   |
|  To remove:   Run 'omnia.sh --uninstall' first, then run install         =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
|  Exiting.                                                                =
   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------=
---+
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
