<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-RollbackDataFlowDiagram">Ro=
llback Data Flow Diagram</h4>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">+-------------------------------------------------=
----------------------------------+
|                  OMNIA CORE CONTAINER ROLLBACK - DATA FLOW DIAGRAM       =
         |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------=
---------+

    +--------+        +--------+        +--------+        +--------+
    |        |        |        |        | Backup |        |  Core  |
    |  User  |        |OIM Host|        |  Dir   |        |  1.0   |
    |        |        |        |        |        |        |        |
    +---+----+        +---+----+        +---+----+        +---+----+
        |                 |                 |                 |
        | Run omnia.sh    |                 |                 |
        | --rollback      |                 |                 |
        |----------------&gt;|                 |                 |
        |                 | Validate backup |                 |
        |                 | and manifest    |                 |
        |                 |----------------&gt;|                 |
        |                 |                 |                 |
        |                 | Select restore  |                 |
        |                 | point           |                 |
        |                 |                 |                 |
        |                 | Restore inputs, |                 |
        |                 | keys, metadata  |                 |
        |                 | from backup     |                 |
        |                 |----------------------------------&gt;|
        |                 |                 |                 |
        |                 | Stop Core 1.1   |                 |
        |                 |------------------------------.    |
        |                 |                              |    |
        |                 | Start Core 1.0 (Quadlet)     |    |
        |                 |------------------------------'    |
        |                 |                 |                 |
        |                 | Revert oim_metadata.yml            |
        |                 |-----------------------------------&gt;|
        |                 |                 |                 |
        | Rollback        |                 |                 |
        | completed       |                 |                 |
        |&lt;----------------|                 |                 |
        |                 |                 |                 |
    +---+----+        +---+----+        +---+----+        +---+----+
    |        |        |        |        |        |        |        |
    |  User  |        |OIM Host|        | Backup |        |  Core  |
    |        |        |        |        |  Dir   |        |  1.0   |
    +--------+        +--------+        +--------+        +--------+

Legend (Rollback):
- User runs `omnia.sh --rollback`
- Validate backup and manifest
- Restore inputs/keys/metadata from selected backup
- Stop Core 1.1, start Core 1.0
- Revert `oim_metadata.yml` version
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
