 step failure</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Disk space exhaustion during backup</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Medium</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Low</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Pre-flight check for =E2=89=A52GB free space=
</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Container health check timeout</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Medium</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Low</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Configurable timeout (60s default), automati=
c rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Input file format incompatibility</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">High</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Medium</td>
