<h2 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.HighLevelDesignofArchitec=
turalComponents">4. High Level Design of Architectural Components</h2>
<h3 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.1DesignComponent=E2=80=93=
UpgradeOrchestrator">4.1 Design Component =E2=80=93 Upgrade Orchestrator</h=
3>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.1.1ComponentDescription/P=
urpose">4.1.1 Component Description / Purpose</h4>
<p>The Upgrade Orchestrator is the central coordination component implement=
ed within <code>omnia.sh</code>. It manages the entire upgrade lifecycle fr=
om pre-validation through post-upgrade verification, ensuring atomic operat=
ions with automatic rollback on failure.</p>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.1.2ComponentDesignConstra=
intsandAssumptions">4.1.2 Component Design Constraints and Assumptions</h4>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.1.2.1Constraints">4.1.2.1=
 Constraints</h5>
<ul>
 <li>Must execute on OIM host with sudo/root privileges</li>
 <li>Requires network access to Docker Hub for image pull</li>
 <li>Single upgrade operation at a time (lock file enforcement)</li>
 <li>Target version must be exactly one minor version ahead (2.0 =E2=86=92 =
2.1)</li>
</ul>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.1.2.2Assumptions">4.1.2.2=
 Assumptions</h5>
<ul>
 <li><code>omnia.sh</code> script is present and executable on OIM host</li=
>
 <li>Container runtime (Podman/Docker) is operational</li>
 <li><code>/opt/omnia</code> volume is mounted and writable</li>
</ul>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.1.3ComponentDesign">4.1.3=
 Component Design</h4>
<p><strong>State Machine:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">+---------+     +----------+     +----------+     =
+----------+
|  IDLE   |----&gt;|VALIDATING|----&gt;| APPROVED |----&gt;| BACKING  |
+---------+     +----------+     +----------+     |   UP     |
     ^               |                            +----+-----+
     |               v                                 |
     |          [FAILED]                               v
     |               |                           +----------+
     |               v                           |MIGRATING |
     |          +---------+                      +----+-----+
     +----------|ROLLED   |&lt;--------------------------+
                | BACK    |                           v
                +---------+&lt;------------------+----------+
                     ^                        | SWAPPING |
                     |                        +----+-----+
                     |                             |
                     |         +----------+        v
                     +---------|VALIDATING|&lt;--+----------+
                               |  POST    |   | UPGRADED |
                               +----+-----+   +----------+
                                    |
                                    v
                               +---------+
                               |COMPLETE |
                               +---------+
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Key Operations:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Operation</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Input</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Output</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Error Handling</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>validate_prerequisites()</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">OIM host state</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Validation result</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Exit with checklist</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>prompt_approval()</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Feature list, version info</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">User confirmation</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Exit on rejection</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>coordinate_backup()</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Backup destination</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Backup manifest</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Exit on failure</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>execute_migration()</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Playbook paths</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Migration status</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>swap_containers()</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Container versions</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Swap status</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>validate_upgrade()</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Expected state</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Validation result</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Trigger rollback</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.1.4SecurityConsiderations=
andTestPlan">4.1.4 Security Considerations and Test Plan</h4>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.1.4.1SecurityDesignObject=
ives">4.1.4.1 Security Design Objectives</h5>
<ul>
 <li>Enforce sudo/root privilege requirement</li>
 <li>Prevent unauthorized automated execution (require interactive confirma=
tion)</li>
 <li>Audit log all upgrade operations to <code>/opt/omnia/logs/upgrade.log<=
/code></li>
 <li>Validate image integrity before container swap</li>
</ul>
