Scalability">4.1.5 Resource Utilization and Scalability</h4>
<ul>
 <li><strong>CPU</strong>: Minimal (shell script orchestration)</li>
 <li><strong>Memory</strong>: &lt; 100MB during execution</li>
 <li><strong>Disk</strong>: Requires =E2=89=A52GB for backup storage</li>
 <li><strong>Network</strong>: ~500MB for image pull (one-time)</li>
</ul>
