<h3 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.2DesignComponent=E2=80=93=
BackupManager">4.2 Design Component =E2=80=93 Backup Manager</h3>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.2.1ComponentDescription/P=
urpose">4.2.1 Component Description / Purpose</h4>
<p>The Backup Manager creates and validates timestamped backups of all crit=
ical Omnia configuration and state files before upgrade operations, enablin=
g reliable rollback.</p>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.2.2ComponentDesignConstra=
intsandAssumptions">4.2.2 Component Design Constraints and Assumptions</h4>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.2.2.1Constraints">4.2.2.1=
 Constraints</h5>
<ul>
 <li>Backup destination must have =E2=89=A52GB free space</li>
 <li>Backup must complete atomically (all-or-nothing)</li>
 <li>Backup must be verifiable for integrity</li>
</ul>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.2.2.2Assumptions">4.2.2.2=
 Assumptions</h5>
<ul>
 <li>Input files are in expected locations under <code>/opt/omnia/input/</c=
ode></li>
 <li>Metadata file structure is consistent</li>
 <li>Metadata file exists at <code>/opt/omnia/.data/oim_metadata.yml</code>=
</li>
</ul>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.2.3ComponentDesign">4.2.3=
 Component Design</h4>
<p><strong>Backup Directory Structure:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">/opt/omnia/backups/upgrade_&lt;timestamp&gt;/
+-- input/                   # Complete input directory copy
|   +-- project_default/
|       +-- omnia_config.yml
|       +-- ...
+-- configs/                 # Container configuration files
+-- metadata/
    +-- oim_metadata.yml     # Version and state metadata
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.2.4SecurityConsiderations=
andTestPlan">4.2.4 Security Considerations and Test Plan</h4>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.2.4.1SecurityDesignObject=
ives">4.2.4.1 Security Design Objectives</h5>
<ul>
 <li>Preserve file permissions in backup</li>
 <li>Protect sensitive files with restricted permissions</li>
 <li>Prevent backup directory traversal attacks</li>
</ul>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.2.4.2ManualSecurityUnitTe=
stingPlan">4.2.4.2 Manual Security Unit Testing Plan</h5>
