<h3 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.3DesignComponent=E2=80=93=
MigrationEngine">4.3 Design Component =E2=80=93 Migration Engine</h3>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.3.1ComponentDescription/P=
urpose">4.3.1 Component Description / Purpose</h4>
<p>The Migration Engine transforms Omnia 2.0 configuration files to Omnia 2=
.1 format through Ansible playbooks, handling schema changes, deprecated op=
tions, and new required fields.</p>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.3.2ComponentDesignConstra=
intsandAssumptions">4.3.2 Component Design Constraints and Assumptions</h4>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.3.2.1Constraints">4.3.2.1=
 Constraints</h5>
<ul>
 <li>Must support all valid 2.0 input configurations</li>
 <li>Migration must be idempotent (safe to re-run)</li>
 <li>Original files preserved in backup before modification</li>
</ul>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.3.2.2Assumptions">4.3.2.2=
 Assumptions</h5>
<ul>
 <li>Input files conform to Omnia 2.0 schema</li>
 <li>Ansible is available within the Omnia core container</li>
</ul>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.3.3ComponentDesign">4.3.3=
 Component Design</h4>
<p><strong>Playbook Hierarchy:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">upgrade_omnia.yml              # Executed inside C=
ore 1.1 container after container swap
+-- upgrade_oim.yml            # OIM-specific migrations
|   +-- Read existing 2.0 input files from /opt/omnia/input/
|   +-- Transform input file schemas 2.0 -&gt; 2.1
|   +-- Add new required fields with sensible defaults
|   +-- Remove deprecated options with warnings
|   +-- Write updated 2.1 input files
+-- upgrade_cluster.yml        # Cluster guidance generation
    +-- Analyze current cluster state
    +-- Generate reprovisioning checklist
    +-- Display post-upgrade workflow guidance

Post-Upgrade Workflow (User-Executed):
+-- prepare_oim.yml          # Prepare OIM for new features
+-- localrepo.yml            # Update local repository with 2.1 packages
+-- discovery.yml            # Reprovision cluster nodes with 2.1 features
    +-- Enables passwordless SSH between nodes (new in 2.1)
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Migration Transformations (2.0 =E2=86=92 2.1):</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Input File</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Transformation</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>software_config.json</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Schema version update</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Update <code>schema_version</code> from 2.0 =
to 2.1</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>omnia_config.yml</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">New required fields</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Add new 2.1 fields with sensible defaults</t=
d>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>network_spec.yml</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Renamed fields</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Map old field names to new 2.1 names</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>provision_config.yml</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Deprecated field removal</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Remove unsupported fields with warning</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">All input files</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Value format changes</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Transform value formats as needed</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<p><strong>Input File Migration Process:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">+-------------------------------------------------=
----------------------------+
|                    INPUT FILE MIGRATION (upgrade_oim.yml)                =
   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------=
---+
|                                                                          =
   |
|  /opt/omnia/input/ (2.0 format)          /opt/omnia/input/ (2.1 format)  =
  |
|  +-------------------------+             +-------------------------+     =
   |
|  | software_config.json    |------------&gt;| software_config.json    |  =
      |
|  | omnia_config.yml        |  Transform  | omnia_config.yml        |     =
   |
|  | network_spec.yml        |------------&gt;| network_spec.yml        |  =
      |
|  | provision_config.yml    |             | provision_config.yml    |     =
   |
|  +-------------------------+             +-------------------------+     =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
|  Backup preserved at: /opt/omnia/backups/upgrade_&lt;timestamp&gt;/      =
         |
|                                                                          =
   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------=
---+
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<p><strong>Post-Upgrade Cluster Reprovisioning:</strong></p>
<p>After <code>upgrade_omnia.yml</code> completes, users must run the follo=
wing playbooks to enable new Omnia 2.1 features:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Step</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Playbook</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Purpose</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">1</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>prepare_oim.yml</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Prepare OIM environment for 2.1 features</td=
>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">2</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>localrepo.yml</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Update local repository with 2.1 packages/im=
ages</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">3</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>discovery.yml</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Reprovision cluster nodes with new configura=
tions</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<p><strong>New Features Requiring Reprovisioning:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Feature</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Enabled By</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Passwordless SSH between nodes</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Enables SSH from any node to any other node =
without password</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>discovery.yml</code> via cloud-init</t=
d>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<blockquote>
 <p><strong>Note:</strong> SSH key configuration on OIM remains unchanged. =
New SSH features are applied to cluster nodes during reprovisioning via clo=
ud-init templates.</p>
</blockquote>
