<h3 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.4DesignComponent=E2=80=93=
RollbackController">4.4 Design Component =E2=80=93 Rollback Controller</h3>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.4.1ComponentDescription/P=
urpose">4.4.1 Component Description / Purpose</h4>
<p>The Rollback Controller restores the Omnia environment to its pre-upgrad=
e state, either automatically on upgrade failure or manually via <code>omni=
a.sh --rollback</code>. It ensures complete state restoration including con=
tainer version, configuration files, and metadata.</p>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.4.2ComponentDesignConstra=
intsandAssumptions">4.4.2 Component Design Constraints and Assumptions</h4>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.4.2.1Constraints">4.4.2.1=
 Constraints</h5>
<ul>
 <li>Requires valid backup from previous upgrade attempt</li>
 <li>Must restore exact pre-upgrade state</li>
 <li>Rollback must be atomic (all-or-nothing)</li>
</ul>
<h5 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.4.2.2Assumptions">4.4.2.2=
 Assumptions</h5>
<ul>
 <li>Backup directory is intact</li>
 <li>Container runtime is operational</li>
 <li>1.0 container image available locally or pullable from Docker Hub</li>
</ul>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.4.3ComponentDesign">4.4.3=
 Component Design</h4>
<p><strong>Rollback Triggers:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
 <table class=3D"confluenceTable">
  <thead>
   <tr>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Trigger</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Source</th>
    <th class=3D"confluenceTh">Behavior</th>
   </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Automatic</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Upgrade failure at Phase 4-6</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Immediate rollback, no prompt</td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Manual</td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>omnia.sh --rollback</code></td>
    <td class=3D"confluenceTd">Prompt for confirmation, select backup</td>
   </tr>
  </tbody>
 </table>
</div>
<p><strong>Rollback Procedure:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
 <div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
  <pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"bru=
sh: java; gutter: false">+-------------------------------------------------=
----------------------------+
|                        ROLLBACK PROCEDURE                                =
   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------=
---+
|                                                                          =
   |
|  1. LOCATE BACKUP                                                        =
   |
|     +-- Automatic: Use backup from current upgrade session               =
   |
|     +-- Manual: List available backups, prompt for selection             =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
|  2. VALIDATE BACKUP                                                      =
   |
|     +-- Verify backup directory exists                                   =
   |
|     +-- Verify all expected files exist                                  =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
|  3. STOP CURRENT CONTAINER                                               =
   |
|     +-- Graceful stop (SIGTERM, 30s timeout)                             =
   |
|     +-- Force stop if graceful fails (SIGKILL)                           =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
|  4. RESTORE FILES                                                        =
   |
|     +-- Execute rollback_omnia.yml playbook                              =
   |
|     +-- Restore input files from backup                                  =
   |
|     +-- Restore container configs from backup                            =
   |
|     +-- Restore oim_metadata.yml from backup                             =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
|  5. START ORIGINAL CONTAINER                                             =
   |
|     +-- Pull 1.0 image from Docker Hub if not available locally          =
   |
|     +-- Start 1.0 Quadlet unit                                           =
   |
|     +-- Wait for health check (60s timeout)                              =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
|  6. VALIDATE ROLLBACK                                                    =
   |
|     +-- Verify container version is 1.0                                  =
   |
|     +-- Verify container version metadata shows 2.0                      =
   |
|     +-- Verify input files restored correctly                            =
   |
|                                                                          =
   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------=
---+
</pre>
 </div>
</div>
<h4 id=3D"UpgradeOmniacorecontainerfrom2.0to2.1-4.4.4SecurityConsiderations=
andTestPlan">4.4.4 Security Considerations and Test Plan</h4>
